This directory contains configuration assets for the Trezor Firmware Tools VS Code extension.

The extension is available at https://github.com/cepetr/vscode-tf-tools.

Contents:

- `manifest.yaml`: Extension manifest and configuration metadata.
- `debug/`: Launch and debug templates.
- `svd/`: SVD files describing MCU registers.
- `profiles.toml`: Shared xtask build profiles.
- `user-profiles.toml`: Optional local xtask build profile overrides; ignored by Git.
